Commercial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"66a5cea4-bac1-47a7-aaa8-20614f12b85f","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Financial and Operating Officer is responsible for overseeing the finances and operations of Building Digital UK.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-08-30T09:42:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Finance and Operating Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5fa6e29a-f7ab-461f-9b31-4c1cdc99cce0","details":{"body":"<p>The programme director is responsible for the delivery of Project Gigabit and for the BDUK team of local delivery managers.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-05T12:44:33Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Project Gigabit Programme Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"d3599d7c-5653-43fe-894e-62b12a26a072","details":{"body":"<p>The Strategy Director is responsible for the strategy and design of Government’s delivery programmes for broadband connectivity.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-05T13:02:35Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Analysis, Evaluation & Strategy ","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"50be8b4c-9604-4e2a-841c-b55c74168278","details":{"body":"<p>The Commercial Director is responsible for BDUK’s commercial activities and provides commercial leadership to all BDUK programmes and business support services.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-05T12:54:11Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Commercial","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"9aa2123d-3c13-4b5c-b307-203698fef45f","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Digital Information Officer is responsible for the use of technology, data and digital services including internal business transformation and the professional oversight of technology standards.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-05T11:22:47Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Digital Information Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7300fa34-b3d9-4a81-ada3-0ca8807b4d4e","details":{"body":"<p>The Programme Director for the Shared Rural Network is responsible for the delivery of the SRN programme that will see public and private investment in a network of new and existing phone masts to level up connectivity across the UK.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-05T12:47:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Shared Rural Network Programme Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7df15204-d1c6-4712-b578-ec9ad2e1652c","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Transformation and Change is responsible for transforming BDUK into a highly efficient specialist delivery organisation and collaborates across the organisation to drive sustainable and impactful transformation.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-04-05T12:58:14Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Transformation and Change","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"dabfc8af-15f0-4304-9d35-4ce5dddfbd18","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Finance and Human Resources is responsible for BDUK’s Human Resources and Finance functions and manages all of the resource and funding requirements for BDUK.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-03-31T14:49:33Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Finance and Human Resources","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"4d968ba4-9acd-4675-90e8-8265fb155474","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Corporate Operations is responsible for designing and implementing BDUK’s governance and assurance frameworks - as well as supporting BDUKs HR processes, internal communications and Transformation and Change teams. </p>\n\n<p>This role includes: governance, assurance, subsidy control, risk management, internal audit, data protection, HR, transformation and change, and internal communications.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-01-12T13:46:54Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Corporate Operations","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"56eea3d0-379c-4179-b591-61f457161f87","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Engagement and Public Information is responsible for BDUK’s communications. The role covers parliamentary affairs, external engagement, promotions and campaigns, media and internal communications.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-09-23T08:38:05Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Engagement and Public Information ","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c65a5efc-b4c0-463d-8a4d-b823d8d4b936","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Engagement and Public Information is responsible for BDUK’s communications. The role covers parliamentary affairs, external engagement, promotions and campaigns, media and internal communications.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-09-23T08:40:03Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director for Engagement and Public Information ","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"aa85dea7-f968-42fd-a58b-3e90e6f285d5","details":{"body":"<p>The Director for Transformation, Change and Programmes is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>transforming BDUK into a highly efficient specialist delivery organisation collaborating across the organisation to drive sustainable and impactful transformation</li>\n  <li>the delivery of the Shared Rural Network programme that will see public and private i